AEME

Aerial Evaluation & Measurement Engine

# scripts structure (public workspace: E:\arena_public)

This document tracks the current script set in the public repository copy.
It intentionally reflects public-safe content only.

## Root files
- `scripts/master.py` (compatibility wrapper; CLI-first path is `arena run`)
- `scripts/phase_config.py` (shim for `arena.lib.phase_config`)
- `scripts/structure` (this file)

## ADS-B aggregation
- `scripts/adsb/aggregators/adsb_aggregator.py`
- `scripts/adsb/aggregators/adsb_csv_patcher.py`
- `scripts/adsb/aggregators/adsb_eval_pk_aggregator.py`
- `scripts/adsb/aggregators/adsb_local_traffic_proxy_gen.py`

