## config and secrets
- `scripts/config/phases.txt`
- `scripts/config/phases_v3_airspy_baseline.txt`
- `scripts/config/settings.toml`
- `scripts/secrets/opensky_credentials.example.json` (public template only)

## Public repository notes
- No private credentials are stored in `scripts/secrets/`.
- CLI/package path is the primary interface (`arena ...`), not direct script execution.
- Shared library logic is under `src/arena/lib` and imported as `arena.lib.*`.
